--[[
    x64 Native UI Mode

    All UI functions are registered natively by UIScriptNative.cpp.
    This script only defines constants and loads form scripts.

    CLU_Call wrapper functions have been REMOVED.
    Lua calls native C++ functions directly via lua_register().

    Functions available natively (from UIScriptNative.cpp):
    - UI_LoadScript, UI_CreateForm, UI_CreateCompent, etc.
    - All UI_* functions are registered globally
    - ARGB, GetTextureID, etc.
]]--

